{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#7713: v-bind with null on slot will crash the app",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:25:00.895561+00:00",
  "text": "v-bind with null on slot will crash the app\n\n### Vue version\n\nv3.3.0-alpha.4\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://sfc.vuejs.org/#\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nWait page loading, then we will see an error: `Cannot read properties of null (reading 'key')`\n\n### What is expected?\n\nDo not crash, and point out `v-bind` should working with an object.\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nCrashed\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n_No response_",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "🔩 p2-edge-case"
  ],
